OL,3,CBlack women ignored and 'not taken
OL,4,Cseriously' in maternity care, MPs say
OL,6,FBlack women in England are being
OL,7,Fignored when it comes to maternity
OL,8,Fcare, with their concerns "not taken
OL,9,Fseriously", MPs have said.
OL,11,FThe issue is "reinforced by bias and
OL,12,Fstereotyping underpinned, in some
OL,13,Fcases, by racist assumptions",
OL,14,Faccording to a new report by the
OL,15,FHealth and Social Care Committee.
