OL,3,CBlack women ignored and 'not taken
OL,4,Cseriously' in maternity care, MPs say
OL,6,FThe investigation found that black
OL,7,Fwomen still face "disproportionately
OL,8,Fpoor outcomes in maternity care" as a
OL,9,Fresult of "systemic failings in
OL,10,Fleadership, training, data collection,
OL,11,Fand accountability".
OL,13,FThe report describes inequities in
OL,14,Fmaternity care as "unjust" and warns
OL,15,Fit "carries deep human and systemic
OL,16,Fcosts" as well as putting financial
OL,17,Fpressure on health services, and could
OL,18,Fnegatively impact public trust.
