OL,3,CBlack women ignored and 'not taken
OL,4,Cseriously' in maternity care, MPs say
OL,6,FBlack women are 2.3 times more likely
OL,7,Fto die during or in the first year
OL,8,Fafter pregnancy than white women, data
OL,9,Freveal.
OL,11,FThe investigation stresses that the
OL,12,F"crisis in care" for black women is
OL,13,F"happening in the context of a
OL,14,Fmaternity system that is failing women
OL,15,Fmore broadly".
OL,17,FThe report comes after Health
OL,18,FSecretary Wes Streeting announced in
OL,19,FJune a national investigation into
OL,20,Fmaternity care in England following a
OL,21,Fseries of scandals.
