OL,3,CBlack women ignored and 'not taken
OL,4,Cseriously' in maternity care, MPs say
OL,6,FShe said: "Their experiences -
OL,7,Fincluding those of fathers and non-
OL,8,Fbirthing partners - will guide our
OL,9,Fwork and shape the national
OL,10,Frecommendations we will publish.
OL,12,F"We will pay particular attention to
OL,13,Fthe inequalities faced by black and
OL,14,FAsian women and by families from
OL,15,Fmarginalised groups, whose voices have
OL,16,Ftoo often been overlooked."
