OL,4,Cseriously' in maternity care, MPs say
OL,6,FMs Hamilton added: "In-built
OL,7,Fstructural racism in maternity
OL,8,Fservices repeatedly fails black women.
OL,10,F"Acknowledging this and addressing
OL,11,Fracial disparities in maternal
OL,12,Foutcomes must be one of the
OL,13,Finvestigation's core aims.
OL,15,F"This has to be the turning point for
OL,16,FEngland's maternity services and
OL,17,Fparticularly for black women if we are
OL,18,Fto achieve equity."
