OL,3,CBlack women ignored and 'not taken
OL,4,Cseriously' in maternity care, MPs say
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,7,FHealth and Social Care said: "Racism
OL,8,Fin any form is completely unacceptable
OL,9,Fand we are determined to reduce the
OL,10,Fshocking disparities that this report
OL,11,Faddresses.
OL,13,F"Every woman deserves safe,
OL,14,Fcompassionate care and that's why the
OL,15,FHealth and Social Care Secretary
OL,16,Fcommissioned a rapid investigation to
OL,17,Fstart tackling maternity failings, so
OL,18,Fthat no more families have to suffer.
