OL,6,F"As part of the investigation,
OL,7,FBaroness Amos will publish
OL,8,Frecommendations to reduce
OL,9,Finequalities, including racism and
OL,10,Fdiscrimination in maternity and
OL,11,Fneonatal care across the country.
OL,13,F"We're already taking action to
OL,14,Fimprove maternity care, including
OL,15,Flaunching an anti-discrimination
OL,16,Fprogramme, training thousands more
OL,17,Fmidwives, and introducing new
OL,18,Fstandards to tackle leading causes of
OL,19,Fmaternal mortality."
